title: 162 - F9 "Saved Theaters"
description: On today's ship is sailed by the one and only Tony Digs. Tone and the boys jump right back into the F9 talk as the group is divided on if/when they will ever go to theaters and see it. After the F9 talk the boys jump right into the packed Pod FOD which is assembled from all things around the internet including the first pictures of Kurt Warner's new doc, a giant python escaping in a mall, the first ever vertically broken penis, and much more. Don't forget to subscribe to YouTube.com/thepodpmi to watch full episodes of The Pod, and send your questions to @ThePodPMI on twitter and Instagram. We appreciate you all for listening, and hope you have an incredible weekend. We'll see you Wednesday.
